## Change Capo [/guitar-tabs/{id}/capo/{capo}]

+ Parameter 

    + id: "674579b33d100f6f68ab31e1" (string) - an unique identifier of the tab
    
+ Parameter 

    + capo: 2 (number) - the fret to put the capo on

